description: <p>Montezuma is a script font which draws \
  inspiration from 1960s beauty product ads. Its \
  sweeping strokes lend to a feel of joy and elegance, \
  making it ideal for display uses that require a little \
  drama, "joie de vivre" or Joy of Life. Best settings \
  are at medium to large text sizes for optimal \
  readability.</p>
  
